  "title": "Business Development (Insurance)",
  "description": "<p>Distribution</p><p>Assist the Head and team to:</p><p>• Onboarding of new agencies and FA</p><p>• Liaison between Agents and Underwriters to address Agents' queries</p><p>• Updating and maintain Agency records</p><p>• Working with the Head and own Team Leader to establish best practices and</p><p>processes to ensure that the team meet the company’s service standards set.</p><p>Channel Performance</p><p>Assist the Head and team to:</p><p>• Compile, analyze and prepare monthly reports required and present during</p><p>monthly meetings and business reviews to be in line with intermediary</p><p>agreements.</p><p>• Ensure that sanction checks are conducted.</p><p>• Update and maintain the records, schedules, statistics, etc.</p><p>• Stay current on market conditions and to share findings and updates with all</p><p>members of the team as appropriate.</p><p>Channel / Relationship Management / Quality Service Standards</p><p>• Maintain and manage distribution email by forwarding cases to the relevant</p><p>parties</p><p>• Work with policy admin team to ensure accurate and timely delivery of</p><p>intermediaries’ document</p><p>• Act as a liaison between agents and underwriters/other departments for any</p><p>feedback which are received</p><p>• Render assistance to the Corporate Services team during Agency / Intermediary</p><p>events</p><p>Staff Training & Development</p><p>• To adopt a holistic approach based on the Corporate Values to contribute to the</p><p>Company’s success</p><p>• To conscientiously attend training to develop self within the organization where</p><p>required.</p><p>• Regularly review and evaluate own performance to ensure compliance with</p><p>established company policies and on track to attaining the goals and objectives</p><p>set, while demonstrating the corporate values.</p><p>• To proactively adopt and constantly practice the Corporate Values and strongly</p><p>encourage other team member’s behavior.</p>",
